data.description: Welcome to this inviting 3-bedroom manufactured home plus an office located in Prairie Greens!  Equipped with all appliances, including the washer and dryer!  This residence offers a stunning mountain views from its large deck, situated on a desirable corner lot. Enjoy the ultimate in leisure and recreation with access to a swimming pool, Club House, fitness center, basketball courts, playgrounds, and picnic areas. The two of the three bedrooms feature walk-in closets, while the large master suite and expansive living room create the perfect blend of comfort and style for your next home.  This is a land lease community and Buyer will need to get approved for that lease from the HOA.
